reviews.comment: Stumbled on this hairdresser by chance, so glad that I did! Such a lovely, sweet person, haircut was great, a great experience. Will definitely be going back and telling friends & family.

Would highly recommend this salon. I booked a last minute blow-dry and showed the barber a picture of what I wanted. He was amazing and highly skilled and did a great job on my hair. I was very happy and would definitely go back again.
reviews.venueReply: Thank you so much for your kind words! We look forward to seeing you again soon.

reviews.comment: I went in for a haircut and had such a great experience with Marcus. He was amazing, warm, welcoming, and incredibly skilled. I came in with an idea, and he took the time to ask the right questions, give thoughtful advice, and really understand what I wanted to achieve. I felt listened to and completely confident in his hands. I absolutely love the result and would 100% recommend him to anyone!
reviews.venueReply: We appreciate your wonderful feedback! Marcus is thrilled to hear you loved your haircut. See you next time!

reviews.comment: Alex is great - very professional and friendly. The beard trim was perfect.
reviews.venueReply: Thanks for choosing us, Dani! We are glad Alex took great care of you.

reviews.comment: Fantastic experience with James. He listened well to what I wanted and gave helpful advice and tips for future visits to maintain the style I want!
Best hot towel shave I have ever had. Alex is a true professional and made me feel completely relaxed. The attention to detail was incredible.
reviews.venueReply: Thank you Tom! We are delighted you enjoyed the experience. Come back soon!

reviews.comment: Marcus gave me exactly what I asked for. Clean fade, perfect lineup. Great atmosphere and professional service throughout.
James is my go-to barber now. Always consistent, always professional. He knows exactly how I like my hair and delivers every time.
reviews.venueReply: We appreciate your loyalty, David! James is happy to be your regular barber.

reviews.comment: Alex transformed my beard. He really knows what he is doing and gave me great advice on maintaining it at home. Will definitely be back.
Great cut, great service. Marcus took his time and made sure everything was perfect. The whole team is friendly and professional.
reviews.venueReply: Thanks Ryan! We are proud of our team and glad you had a great experience.

products.title: Shaving Bowl Shaving Bowl
products.description: A shaving bowl is an essential grooming accessory designed to create a rich, smooth lather for a comfortable shaving experience. Crafted from durable, high-quality materials, it helps evenly mix shaving cream or soap, ensuring a thick and creamy foam. Its ergonomic shape provides a comfortable grip and prevents spills, making it ideal for both home and professional barbershop use. Perfect for traditional wet shaving, a shaving bowl enhances precision, comfort, and overall grooming quality.

products.title: BabyblissPro Gold Skeleton Outliner
products.description: The BabylissPRO Gold Skeleton Outliner is a high-performance professional trimmer designed for sharp lines, detailed edging, and precise outlining. Featuring a powerful motor and an exposed 360° skeleton blade, it provides maximum visibility and control for flawless results. The gold-finish metal housing adds durability and a premium look, while its ergonomic design ensures comfort during extended use. Ideal for barbers and stylists, this outliner delivers accuracy, speed, and professional-grade performance every time.

products.title: BabyblissPro Gold VibeFx
products.description: The BabylissPRO Gold VibeFX is a powerful, professional massaging tool designed to enhance comfort and relaxation during grooming services. Equipped with high-speed vibration technology, it helps reduce muscle tension and improves client comfort during haircuts, shaves, and facial treatments. Its sleek all-metal gold housing offers durability and a premium feel, while the cordless design ensures ease of use and flexibility. Ideal for barbers and stylists, the Gold VibeFX elevates the grooming experience with performance and luxury combined.

products.title: Skeleton FX Black
products.description: The SkeletonFX Black is a professional-grade outliner engineered for sharp detailing, clean edges, and precise line work. Featuring a high-performance motor and an exposed 360° skeleton blade, it offers maximum visibility for ultimate accuracy and control. The sleek black metal housing delivers durability with a modern, stylish finish, while its ergonomic design ensures comfort during extended use. Ideal for barbers and stylists, the SkeletonFX Black provides powerful performance and flawless results every time.

products.title: Babyliss Gold Shaver
products.description: The Babyliss Gold Shaver is a high-performance professional grooming tool designed for ultra-smooth, close shaving. Equipped with powerful motor technology and precision-engineered foil blades, it delivers a clean, irritation-free finish. The durable all-metal gold housing offers a premium look and long-lasting performance, while its ergonomic design ensures comfort and control during use. Ideal for barbers and stylists, the Babyliss Gold Shaver is perfect for finishing fades, clean shaves, and detailed grooming with flawless results.

products.title: 2IN1 Hair Styler Modelling Comb & Beard straightener
products.description: The 2-in-1 Hair Styler Modelling Comb & Beard Straightener is a versatile grooming tool designed for effortless styling and precision control. Combining a heated straightening comb with beard-taming technology, it smooths, shapes, and styles hair and facial hair with ease. Its advanced heat distribution ensures safe, even styling while reducing frizz and damage. Lightweight, ergonomic, and easy to use, this tool is ideal for daily grooming, offering salon-quality results at home or on the go.

products.title: Babyliss Nose and Ear Trimmer
products.description: The Babyliss Nose and Ear Trimmer is a compact and efficient grooming tool designed for safe and precise trimming of unwanted nose and ear hair. Featuring a gentle yet powerful cutting system, it ensures a smooth, irritation-free experience. Its ergonomic design allows easy handling and control, while the durable blades provide long-lasting performance. Ideal for everyday grooming, this trimmer offers quick, hygienic, and hassle-free maintenance at home or on the go.

products.title: Pro Lather Hot Lather Machine W/Bonus Tray & W/ 2 Shave Cream
products.description:
Pro Lather Hot Lather Machine (with Bonus Tray & 2 Shave Creams)
The Pro Lather Hot Lather Machine is a professional grooming essential designed to deliver warm, rich lather for a smooth and comfortable shaving experience. It heats shaving cream evenly, providing consistent temperature and luxurious foam for enhanced skin comfort. The included bonus tray ensures neat and organized use, while the two shave creams add extra value for immediate operation. Ideal for barbershops and home grooming, this machine combines efficiency, convenience, and professional-grade performance.
